Geekspeak is a type of [[slang]] used by [[geeks]], especially [[computer]] geeks. It incorporates several terms derived from [[science fiction]], as well as [[neologism]]s and [[grammatical|grammar]] quirks, and is frequently found in combination with [[computer jargon]].

The [[Jargon File]] is commonly considered the closest thing to a definite reference for geekspeak available.

